<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231589>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Gaurax mycophagus Nartshuk sp. n. (A – E, holotype; F, paratype). A. epandrium and hypandrium, ventral view. B. epandrium, lateral view. C. epandrium, posterodorsal view. D. epandrium, posterior view. E. hypandrium and phallic complex, lateral view. F. habitus, female. Scale bar = 0.1 mm (A – E) and 0.5 mm (F). Abbreviations: cerc = cercus, ep = epandrium, hyp = hypandrium, ph = phallus, postg = postgonite, preg = pregonite, sur = surstylus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/231589/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

